{"tid":166156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周末翻風落雨暖變涼 料一日驟降7度","createTime":"2017-03-22T01:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T01:57:56.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c292cd4f10f443964b4416c8d74030bd09b9c173","tid":166156,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:42:06.000Z","msg":"本港近日經歷炎熱天氣後，周末期間將翻風兼落雨，氣溫顯著下降；天文台指，一股東北季候風的補充下周初會抵港，市區氣溫會由周六（25日）下午最高的22&deg;C（和暖），逐步跌至周日下午最低的15&deg;C（清涼），即一日左右下跌7度，周一早上仍低見15&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n此外，因華南周末期間受高空擾動影響，該區天氣將轉為不穩定及有雷雨；本港天色和雨勢會由周六的「短暫時間有陽光，稍後有幾陣雨」，轉為周日「多雲，間中有雨」。<br />\n<br />\n短期天氣方面，天文台指，東北季候風會在未來一兩天影響華南沿岸，該區風勢較大及有幾陣雨；本港未來一兩天將大致多雲及有幾陣雨，沿岸有霧或薄霧，一連5日濕度均高達95%。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56461416&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56461416%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170322&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=d89f9f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56461416%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170322&h=d5083172\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56461416&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170322</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/375u8x4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F375u8x4d&h=d34fb648&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75b2ca59c87e0902c07463a0777ee1b815fe35e1","tid":166156,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"屌3月22"},{"pid":"d9fb0df60ddf280b7cdc4cd35321c21c03cc172f","tid":166156,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /